1
00:02:30,880 --> 00:02:31,760
A hundred years ago,

2
00:02:32,680 --> 00:02:34,120
Luo Hou, Demon Sovereign of Qiumina,

3
00:02:34,560 --> 00:02:36,160
obtained the Turbidity Lock.

4
00:02:37,080 --> 00:02:39,880
He led his clan from the Netherworld
to invade our lands.

5
00:02:41,200 --> 00:02:42,800
The Turbidity Lock cast a spell

6
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:46,120
to drain our essence blood
to fuel his power.

7
00:02:47,440 --> 00:02:48,600
All Five Clans of Mulingor live

8
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:51,800
under Luo Hou's oppression.

9
00:02:53,400 --> 00:02:54,080
But

10
00:02:55,200 --> 00:02:57,200
I have always believed a legend:

11
00:02:58,400 --> 00:03:00,040
Deep within the Mulingor Oasis

12
00:03:00,320 --> 00:03:02,720
lies a divine sword that can sever
the Turbidity Lock.

13
00:03:03,520 --> 00:03:04,560
To claim it,

14
00:03:05,320 --> 00:03:06,720
one needs the Dragon and Phoenix Beasts

15
00:03:07,040 --> 00:03:07,960
to open the Zone.

16
00:03:09,040 --> 00:03:10,480
Once I hold that divine sword,

17
00:03:11,320 --> 00:03:12,840
I can slay Luo Hou

18
00:03:13,440 --> 00:03:15,000
and change everyone's fate.

19
00:03:22,160 --> 00:03:23,200
Xihe,

20
00:03:24,080 --> 00:03:25,640
you're secretly
practicing swordplay again.

21
00:03:27,080 --> 00:03:29,680
Still chasing that divine sword tale?

22
00:03:32,080 --> 00:03:33,840
The legend must be true.

23
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:37,240
The two beasts have proven it.

24
00:03:37,920 --> 00:03:40,520
They were born with the divine sword.

25
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:43,680
Those chick and worm?

26
00:03:44,280 --> 00:03:46,000
You truly think they are divine beasts?

27
00:03:46,920 --> 00:03:48,400
Ever since you found them,

28
00:03:48,600 --> 00:03:49,800
all they do is eat and sleep.

29
00:03:50,320 --> 00:03:51,760
Have they grown fatter again?

30
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:54,560
I have seen their true forms.

31
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:57,200
Do not trust this disguise.

32
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:58,880
They are divine beasts, after all.

33
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:00,320
If they do not eat more,

34
00:04:00,440 --> 00:04:01,240
how will they ever grow

35
00:04:01,520 --> 00:04:02,320
and slay Luo Hou?

36
00:04:03,120 --> 00:04:04,120
Xihe,

37
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:05,360
stop teasing me.

38
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:07,360
Luo Hou is the Demon Sovereign.

39
00:04:07,680 --> 00:04:09,120
And we are only refugees.

40
00:04:09,680 --> 00:04:10,880
I do not want you to die.

41
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:14,040
It can't get worse than this.

42
00:04:15,120 --> 00:04:16,400
Once we find the divine sword,

43
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:17,400
we

44
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:19,960
won't be bullied
by the Demon Clan again.

45
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:31,520
The demons are here.

46
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:34,080
Hide here.

47
00:04:34,400 --> 00:04:35,360
Do not let them find you.

48
00:04:40,440 --> 00:04:43,880
Luo Hou comes for blood to cultivate.

49
00:04:45,440 --> 00:04:46,560
We tried to resist.

50
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:48,480
But the Demon Clan is too powerful.

51
00:04:49,240 --> 00:04:50,840
They have the Nine Vile Phases.

52
00:04:51,880 --> 00:04:55,040
We once had the Seven Phases,

53
00:04:55,440 --> 00:04:57,960
including Refining,
Foundation, Immortality,

54
00:04:58,400 --> 00:05:02,080
Celestial, Formless, and Purity.

55
00:05:03,320 --> 00:05:05,200
But the Turbidity Lock's spell

56
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:08,000
sealed the ethereal spirit within us.

57
00:05:14,280 --> 00:05:16,120
Under Luo Hou are the Four Demon Lords.

58
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:18,240
Chen Yuan delights in taking lives.

59
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:20,640
Yet Luo Hou made him our warden.

60
00:05:22,320 --> 00:05:24,000
No matter the phase,

61
00:05:24,280 --> 00:05:25,560
once you fight with Qi,

62
00:05:25,760 --> 00:05:27,000
the spell will be activated,

63
00:05:27,400 --> 00:05:28,440
and you'll die a violent death.

64
00:05:29,880 --> 00:05:32,080
We are fodder,
trapped in this refugee camp,

65
00:05:32,960 --> 00:05:34,760
for the Demon Clan's cultivation.

66
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:48,400
His Grace nears the Vile IX Phase,

67
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:50,000
about to break through.

68
00:05:50,360 --> 00:05:52,480
He needs more fresh blood.

69
00:05:53,200 --> 00:05:54,480
All of you

70
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:57,520
are honored to offer your blood.

71
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:30,000
The divine sword

72
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:32,760
is our hope to overthrow all this.

73
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:35,320
But until we find it,

74
00:06:36,200 --> 00:06:38,320
we can only endure in silence.

75
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:40,040
Endure.

76
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:42,920
And endure.

77
00:07:04,160 --> 00:07:04,760
Are you okay?

78
00:07:11,200 --> 00:07:11,800
Careful!

79
00:07:13,440 --> 00:07:14,200
Give me a hand.

80
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:15,960
Senior.

81
00:07:30,080 --> 00:07:30,760
Senior.

82
00:07:31,320 --> 00:07:31,960
It is no use.

83
00:07:32,560 --> 00:07:33,920
They have been drained too often.

84
00:07:34,560 --> 00:07:36,000
They will soon become Blood Mist

85
00:07:36,840 --> 00:07:38,360
and feed Luo Hou.

86
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:39,760
Even so, I hope

87
00:07:40,560 --> 00:07:42,480
they may die with dignity.

88
00:07:45,640 --> 00:07:46,600
All of this

89
00:07:47,120 --> 00:07:47,960
will come to an end.

90
00:07:51,600 --> 00:07:52,240
Come with me.

91
00:08:17,280 --> 00:08:19,280
If Luo Hou reaches the Vile IX Phase,

92
00:08:19,360 --> 00:08:22,240
he will rival a Purity Greatmaster.

93
00:08:22,560 --> 00:08:23,480
By then,

94
00:08:23,720 --> 00:08:24,800
what awaits us

95
00:08:25,320 --> 00:08:27,240
is utter ruin.

96
00:08:28,080 --> 00:08:28,800
Stay calm.

97
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:30,920
Trust Chiyang's plan.

98
00:08:37,280 --> 00:08:38,480
Raise your heads.

99
00:08:40,280 --> 00:08:41,600
As chief of the Luminara Clan,

100
00:08:42,040 --> 00:08:42,840
this mission

101
00:08:43,560 --> 00:08:44,400
will be under my command.

102
00:08:46,320 --> 00:08:47,480
Before Luo Hou breaks through,

103
00:08:47,800 --> 00:08:49,400
he will become weak first.

104
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,200
When the Blood Moon rises,

105
00:08:51,760 --> 00:08:53,600
Luo Hou will begin his seclusion,

106
00:08:53,960 --> 00:08:55,960
the Demon Lords will guard him,

107
00:08:56,280 --> 00:08:57,800
and defenses will be at their weakest.

108
00:08:58,280 --> 00:08:58,720
This

109
00:08:58,800 --> 00:09:01,120
is our only chance to escape.

110
00:09:02,840 --> 00:09:04,200
We'll move in two groups.

111
00:09:05,040 --> 00:09:06,000
The elders and I

112
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:07,520
have chosen the Array Team.

113
00:09:07,840 --> 00:09:09,560
They will set the array in the square.

114
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:11,080
Once the Blood Moon hangs high,

115
00:09:11,360 --> 00:09:12,680
they'll trigger it
and blast the lock stake

116
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:13,800
to break the Zone.

117
00:09:14,280 --> 00:09:14,680
Yes.

118
00:09:16,160 --> 00:09:17,560
The rest will form the Escort Team

119
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:18,920
and wait at the border.

120
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:20,520
Once the Zone loosens,

121
00:09:21,040 --> 00:09:22,280
take the clan and leave at once.

122
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:22,800
Yes.

123
00:09:23,920 --> 00:09:26,400
You are the elite of our clan.

124
00:09:27,040 --> 00:09:27,800
This time,

125
00:09:28,160 --> 00:09:29,160
we must win.

126
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:32,080
Dismissed.

127
00:09:44,680 --> 00:09:45,280
Senior.

128
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:46,360
I want to join the Array Team.

129
00:09:48,120 --> 00:09:48,720
Why?

130
00:09:49,440 --> 00:09:50,880
The Array Team needs better odds.

131
00:09:51,320 --> 00:09:53,840
You think breaking the array
outweighs escorting?

132
00:09:55,400 --> 00:09:56,240
Only by breaking the array

133
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:57,520
is there hope of escape.

134
00:09:58,240 --> 00:10:00,200
I train daily with the sword.
I can handle it.

135
00:10:00,360 --> 00:10:01,360
The plan is set.

136
00:10:01,760 --> 00:10:02,680
Save your strength

137
00:10:03,040 --> 00:10:04,160
for those we are escorting.

138
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:14,080
You took the remnant copy
of Luminara Swordsmanship

139
00:10:14,400 --> 00:10:15,560
in my room, didn't you?

140
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:17,680
So, you knew.

141
00:10:18,400 --> 00:10:19,480
I thought becoming stronger

142
00:10:19,920 --> 00:10:21,280
would let me do greater things.

143
00:10:24,360 --> 00:10:25,680
This is the Clan Sword.

144
00:10:26,640 --> 00:10:27,720
It's called Scorch.

145
00:10:29,280 --> 00:10:30,400
With this sword,

146
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:32,520
let me see how much you've grasped.

147
00:10:36,960 --> 00:10:37,920
Please guide me.

148
00:10:45,400 --> 00:10:45,880
Heavy.

149
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:46,560
Hasty.

150
00:10:46,760 --> 00:10:47,240
Chaotic.

151
00:10:47,960 --> 00:10:49,520
Is this the fruit of your practice?

152
00:10:50,960 --> 00:10:51,600
I've practiced the swordsmanship

153
00:10:51,960 --> 00:10:52,960
day and night.

154
00:10:53,280 --> 00:10:53,960
What is

155
00:10:54,200 --> 00:10:55,120
your practice for?

156
00:10:58,840 --> 00:10:59,680
To break the spell,

157
00:10:59,840 --> 00:11:00,600
kill Luo Hou,

158
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:01,560
and end the demonic turmoil.

159
00:11:02,280 --> 00:11:03,640
But you can't do it alone.

160
00:11:05,240 --> 00:11:06,120
Without our people,

161
00:11:06,680 --> 00:11:08,920
everything the Array Team has done
would mean nothing.

162
00:11:13,600 --> 00:11:14,840
To end the demonic turmoil,

163
00:11:15,080 --> 00:11:16,760
you can't rely on yourself alone.

164
00:11:17,520 --> 00:11:18,280
Why do you train

165
00:11:18,640 --> 00:11:19,800
with the sword?

166
00:11:27,640 --> 00:11:28,880
To protect our people.

167
00:11:29,680 --> 00:11:30,800
I'll join everyone

168
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:32,560
to end the demonic turmoil.

169
00:11:33,840 --> 00:11:35,480
Remember this state of mind.

170
00:11:36,520 --> 00:11:37,760
Try that strike

171
00:11:38,880 --> 00:11:40,040
again.

172
00:12:23,880 --> 00:12:24,680
Please leave

173
00:12:24,880 --> 00:12:25,760
the escort to me.

174
00:12:30,360 --> 00:12:31,080
Even

175
00:12:32,040 --> 00:12:34,640
with the whole clan,

176
00:12:35,080 --> 00:12:36,320
we may still lose.

177
00:12:36,840 --> 00:12:39,040
But we will prevail one day.

178
00:12:39,800 --> 00:12:41,360
One person's flame may die,

179
00:12:41,640 --> 00:12:42,920
but the flames of countless souls

180
00:12:43,520 --> 00:12:44,400
can never be burned out.

181
00:12:45,160 --> 00:12:46,160
The spark endures.

182
00:12:46,760 --> 00:12:47,920
One day, it will ignite the world.

183
00:12:51,520 --> 00:12:52,120
This

184
00:12:52,640 --> 00:12:54,480
is our clan's legacy.

185
00:12:56,520 --> 00:12:57,320
I will remember that.

186
00:13:00,160 --> 00:13:01,520
The swordsmanship you've learned

187
00:13:01,720 --> 00:13:03,080
can draw upon the ethereal energy
exceptionally.

188
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:05,040
Alas, it's just a remnant copy.

189
00:13:05,840 --> 00:13:06,960
You must grasp and perfect

190
00:13:07,080 --> 00:13:08,560
the moves within yourself.

191
00:13:09,240 --> 00:13:10,240
Senior, could you

192
00:13:10,880 --> 00:13:12,240
name the first move

193
00:13:12,600 --> 00:13:13,320
I learned today?

194
00:13:13,960 --> 00:13:14,800
Let's call it

195
00:13:15,480 --> 00:13:16,160
Nightbane.

196
00:13:17,360 --> 00:13:18,640
The darkness has lasted too long.

197
00:13:19,760 --> 00:13:20,720
It's time for the light to return.

198
00:13:20,744 --> 00:13:52,244
(Watch the Latest Donoghue Episodes: www.h-donghua.com)

199
00:13:53,680 --> 00:13:54,400
Everyone,

200
00:13:54,760 --> 00:13:55,720
the Blood Moon is coming.

201
00:13:56,280 --> 00:13:57,440
Insert the sigil stones.

202
00:13:57,680 --> 00:13:58,440
Activate the array!

203
00:14:59,200 --> 00:15:00,240
It's Luo Hou.

204
00:15:08,720 --> 00:15:09,640
The sigil stones!

205
00:15:10,000 --> 00:15:10,920
No!

206
00:15:18,200 --> 00:15:19,600
Who dares disturb me?

207
00:15:20,240 --> 00:15:22,160
I'll kill them at once.

208
00:15:28,160 --> 00:15:29,160
There's movement in the square.

209
00:15:29,520 --> 00:15:30,480
Should we make our move?

210
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:35,640
Something's wrong.

211
00:15:36,280 --> 00:15:37,560
The Zone hasn't weakened.

212
00:15:38,160 --> 00:15:39,000
Trouble!

213
00:15:40,320 --> 00:15:41,440
Everyone, stay calm.

214
00:15:42,040 --> 00:15:42,880
Escort Team, hold position.

215
00:15:42,960 --> 00:15:43,760
Protect our people.

216
00:15:44,560 --> 00:15:45,960
Once the Zone is breached,

217
00:15:46,000 --> 00:15:46,880
evacuate at once.

218
00:15:48,640 --> 00:15:49,040
This...

219
00:15:49,560 --> 00:15:50,160
This is...

220
00:15:50,840 --> 00:15:51,920
It's Luo Hou.

221
00:15:57,600 --> 00:15:58,960
The sigil stones were destroyed.

222
00:16:00,200 --> 00:16:02,440
Is this the power
of the Vile VIII Phase?

223
00:16:04,240 --> 00:16:05,480
The sigil stones are gone.

224
00:16:05,760 --> 00:16:07,200
Let's use our flesh and blood

225
00:16:07,600 --> 00:16:08,680
as the final sigil stones.

226
00:16:09,920 --> 00:16:11,320
We must detonate the sigil array

227
00:16:11,840 --> 00:16:12,760
at all costs!

228
00:16:14,960 --> 00:16:16,080
To your positions!

229
00:16:16,280 --> 00:16:17,160
Activate the array!

230
00:16:20,680 --> 00:16:21,800
You old fools.

231
00:16:22,000 --> 00:16:24,120
You still rebel at death's door.

232
00:16:24,440 --> 00:16:25,920
You like to play, huh?

233
00:16:26,200 --> 00:16:28,560
Fine, let's play.

234
00:16:38,000 --> 00:16:39,360
These old geezers are mine.

235
00:16:39,720 --> 00:16:41,360
The rest who want to die

236
00:16:41,960 --> 00:16:43,000
are yours.

237
00:16:46,000 --> 00:16:47,040
With my blood as the guide,

238
00:16:47,640 --> 00:16:48,760
ignite my clan's soul.

239
00:16:50,120 --> 00:16:51,560
Even if we die today,

240
00:16:52,040 --> 00:16:52,480
we

241
00:16:52,760 --> 00:16:54,680
will surely shake the Turbidity Lock!

242
00:17:17,680 --> 00:17:19,200
Go to hell!

243
00:18:24,800 --> 00:18:26,240
Senior Chiyang!

244
00:18:29,720 --> 00:18:31,800
Has the mission failed?

245
00:18:32,760 --> 00:18:33,680
No.

246
00:18:36,040 --> 00:18:36,960
It's almost done.

247
00:18:39,200 --> 00:18:40,360
You'll sacrifice yourself

248
00:18:40,720 --> 00:18:41,720
to blow up the lock stake!

249
00:18:47,680 --> 00:18:49,160
The clan needs you.

250
00:18:49,880 --> 00:18:52,040
The clan never needed just one.

251
00:18:54,520 --> 00:18:55,840
Today, we have come this far

252
00:18:56,480 --> 00:18:59,240
because we trust in the clan's tomorrow.

253
00:19:00,040 --> 00:19:01,400
Anyone can fall.

254
00:19:02,360 --> 00:19:04,400
But the clan will march on.

255
00:19:05,640 --> 00:19:06,280
Xihe,

256
00:19:07,080 --> 00:19:08,640
hear my final command.

257
00:19:18,120 --> 00:19:18,720
Today,

258
00:19:20,120 --> 00:19:21,520
in the name of the chief,

259
00:19:22,400 --> 00:19:24,360
I pass the clan sword to you.

260
00:19:25,600 --> 00:19:26,560
From this day forth,

261
00:19:27,600 --> 00:19:29,160
you shall carry the will of Luminara,

262
00:19:30,160 --> 00:19:31,480
protect the clan in peril,

263
00:19:32,360 --> 00:19:33,880
pass the torch to future generations,

264
00:19:34,480 --> 00:19:35,840
and fulfill your mission

265
00:19:36,760 --> 00:19:38,200
by killing Luo Hou

266
00:19:38,840 --> 00:19:40,160
and liberating

267
00:19:41,040 --> 00:19:42,440
the Luminara Clan.

268
00:19:52,080 --> 00:19:53,120
In Luo Hou's eyes,

269
00:19:54,200 --> 00:19:55,160
we fear death,

270
00:19:56,080 --> 00:19:58,360
destined to bow
beneath the lock forever.

271
00:19:59,920 --> 00:20:00,880
She is wrong.

272
00:20:02,120 --> 00:20:03,440
At the end of humiliation,

273
00:20:04,080 --> 00:20:05,760
we no longer fear death.

274
00:20:07,600 --> 00:20:09,760
We vow to fight to the bitter end

275
00:20:11,080 --> 00:20:13,000
with indomitable will.

276
00:20:40,960 --> 00:20:42,640
I'm Fengyi Xihe.

277
00:20:44,000 --> 00:20:45,320
I thus accept the sword.

278
00:21:10,880 --> 00:21:11,440
This is...

279
00:21:12,040 --> 00:21:12,880
The Zone is open! Go!

280
00:21:13,040 --> 00:21:13,680
Run!

281
00:21:14,760 --> 00:21:15,400
Run!

282
00:21:15,400 --> 00:21:16,040
Keep up!

283
00:21:16,040 --> 00:21:16,680
Keep up back there!

284
00:21:16,680 --> 00:21:17,320
Run!

285
00:21:17,320 --> 00:21:17,960
Keep up!

286
00:21:20,800 --> 00:21:21,440
Move faster!

287
00:21:22,160 --> 00:21:22,840
Run!

288
00:21:22,960 --> 00:21:23,840
Quick, keep up!

289
00:21:24,480 --> 00:21:25,080
Hurry, keep up!

290
00:21:25,080 --> 00:21:26,080
We're almost out!

